 Rock Werchter 2025：Iggy Pop、Underworld 和 Gracie Abrams 领衔新阵容https://www.nme.com/news/music/rock-werchter-2025-iggy-pop-underworld-and-gracie-abrams-lead-new-line-up-additions-3819822?u tm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=rock-werchter-2025-iggy-pop-underworld-and-gracie-abrams-lead-new-line-up-additionsLiberty Dunworth Fri, 06 Dec 2024 16:58:20 +0000 Music NewsNewsAlternativeIndieLive Music NewsMetalPopRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3819822 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Werchter@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="伊基·波普、格雷西·艾布拉姆斯和黑社会" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Werchter@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Werchter@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Werchter@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Werchter@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Werchter@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Werchter@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他们加入了之前宣布的领军人物 Linkin Park、Green Day、Sam Fender 和 Olivia Rodrigo 的行列</p><p>《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rock-werchter-2025-iggy-pop-underworld-and-gracie-abrams-lead-new-line-up-additions-3819822">Rock Werchter 2025：Iggy Pop、Underworld 和 Gracie Abrams 领衔的新阵容》</a>首次在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上亮相。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Werchter@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="伊基·波普、格雷西·艾布拉姆斯和黑社会" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Werchter@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Werchter@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Werchter@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Werchter@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Werchter@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Werchter@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Rock Werchter 宣布了将在 2025 年版音乐节上表演的新名单，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/iggy-pop">Iggy Pop</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gracie-abrams">Gracie Abrams</a>等。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/iggy-pop-cover-interview-2022-every-loser-3358737">伊基·波普 (Iggy Pop)：“我以为一旦我年满 65 岁，事情就会平静下来。但事实并非如此”</a></strong></li></ul><p>明年的音乐节将于 7 月 3 日至 6 日在比利时 Werchter Festivalpark 举行，纪念首届音乐节 50 周年。</p><p>第一波艺术家在几周前得到确认，摇滚重量级乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/linkin-park">Linkin Park</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/green-day">Green Day</a>将分别在周四 (3) 和周五 (4) 天担任主角，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sam-fender">萨姆·芬德 (Sam Fender)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-rodrigo">奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo)</a>则作为主角在主舞台上表演周六（5）和周日（6）。</p><p>对于 Linkin Park 来说，这是他们自今年早些时候<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/linkin-park-announce-new-singer-album-and-world-tour-3791116">宣布</a>以 Dead Sara 的 Emily Armstrong 担任主唱并推出新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/linkin-park-from-zero-review-3811752">《From Zero》</a>回归以来的第一个音乐节。对于 Green Day 来说，这是朋克三重奏计划于 2025 年举办的众多即将推出的节目之一，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/download-2025-announced-stacked-line-up-with-green-day-sleep-token-korn-and-more-tickets-3812026">英国下载节上的头条节目</a>。</p><p>对于萨姆·芬德 (Sam Fender) 来说，这一消息是在他宣布备受期待的第三张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/sam-fenders-people-watching-review-3812982">《People Watching》时宣布的，</a>而对于奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo) 来说，这一消息是在她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-announces-2024-guts-world-tour-shows-buy-tickets-3497458">大规模的“胆量”世界巡演</a>之后发布的，这使她成为音乐节有史以来最年轻的头条新闻。</p><p>不久之后，更多的名字被添加进来，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c">Fontaines DC</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/amyl-and-the-sniffers">Amyl And The Sniffers</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/raye">RAYE</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/girl-in-red">Girl In Red</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/barry-cant-swim">Barry Can&#39;t Swim</a> 。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">摇滚韦希特 (Rock Werchter) 势头正盛！这是<a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/RW25?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#RW25</a>的 13 个新名字<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f4a5.png" alt="💥" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p><p> 7 月 3 日星期四：Deftones、Iggy Pop、Jacob Collier<br /> 7 月 4 日星期五：《黑夜传说》、《紫色迪斯科机器》、马克·安博尔<br />7 月 5 日星期六：马里布州、阿门拉、布兰科·怀特、金带<br />7 月 6 日星期日：Gracie Abrams、Dean Lewis、GOOSE <a href="https://t.co/r0L0DuXRu7">pic.twitter.com/r0L0DuXRu7</a></p><p> — Rock Werchter (@RockWerchter) <a href="https://twitter.com/RockWerchter/status/1865010752156737566?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 12 月 6 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>现在，该音乐节已确认更多名字加入 2025 年 Rock Werchter。</p><p>现在， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/deftones">Deftones</a> 、Iggy Pop 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jacob-collier">Jacob Collier</a>是音乐节第一天添加的三个新名字 (3)，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/underworld">Underworld</a> 、Purple Disco Machine 和 Mark Ambor 现已确定在周五举行。</p><p>在最后两天里，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/maribou-state">马里布州立大学</a>、阿门拉、布兰科·怀特和戈德班德已被添加到周六的阵容中，而格雷西·艾布拉姆斯、迪恩·刘易斯和古斯是被锁定的三个新名字，以帮助结束这场比赛。最后一天。</p><p>音乐节的门票现已开始销售，预计很快会有更多的名字加入到演出阵容中。组织者的最新消息称，周四的一日票已售罄，但周五、周六和周日的组合票和一日票仍然有售。</p><p> <a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Frock-werchter-festival-tickets%2Fartist%2F1955326" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处购买门票</a>，并查看上面的最新更新。</p><p>参加<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/foo-fighters-and-dua-lipa-announced-as-rock-werchter-2024-headliners-3537761">2024 年音乐节的</a>表演者包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-pretenders">The Pretenders</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-odell">Tom Odell</a> 、Nathaniel Rateliff 和 The Night Sweats，以及头条新闻<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">Dua Lipa</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/foo-fighters">Foo Fighters</a> 。早在 2023 年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/red-hot-chili-peppers">Red Hot Chili Peppers</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/queens-of-the-stone-age">Queens Of The Stone Age</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arctic-monkeys">Arctic Monkeys</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/muse">Muse</a>就与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">Liam Gallagher</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/iggy-pop">Iggy Pop</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-1975">The 1975</a>等乐队一起演出。</p><p> 《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rock-werchter-2025-iggy-pop-underworld-and-gracie-abrams-lead-new-line-up-additions-3819822">Rock Werchter 2025：Iggy Pop、Underworld 和 Gracie Abrams 领衔的新阵容》</a>首次在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上亮相。</p> ;
休·格兰特送给《毁灭》童星一盒雪茄作为包装礼物：“他的母亲很生气” https://www.nme.com/news/film/hugh-grant-gave-the-undoing-child-star-a-box-of-cigars-as-wrap-present-3819794?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=休·格兰特送了一盒雪茄作为包装礼物Elizabeth AubreyFri, 06 Dec 2024 16:54:44 +0000 Film NewsNewsTV News https://www.nme.com/?p=3819794 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Hugh-Grant-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Gerald-Matzka_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="休·格兰特" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Hugh-Grant-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Gerald-Matzka_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Hugh-Grant-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Gerald-Matzka_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Hugh-Grant-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Gerald-Matzka_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Hugh-Grant-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Gerald-Matzka_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Hugh-Grant-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Gerald-Matzka_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Hugh-Grant-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Gerald-Matzka_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位童星收到格兰特的礼物时才14岁</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/hugh-grant-gave-the-undoing-child-star-a-box-of-cigars-as-wrap-present-3819794">休·格兰特送给“The Undoing”童星一盒雪茄作为包装礼物：“他的母亲很愤怒”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Hugh-Grant-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Gerald-Matzka_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="休·格兰特" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Hugh-Grant-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Gerald-Matzka_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Hugh-Grant-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Gerald-Matzka_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Hugh-Grant-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Gerald-Matzka_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Hugh-Grant-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Gerald-Matzka_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Hugh-Grant-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Gerald-Matzka_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Hugh-Grant-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Gerald-Matzka_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hugh-grant">休·格兰特</a>透露，他送给这位<i>《毁灭》</i>童星一盒雪茄作为包装礼物——这让他的母亲“非常愤怒”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/heretic-review-hugh-grant-horror-3807614">“异端”评论：休·格兰特在华而不实的恐怖中用礼貌换取威胁</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位演员在<a href="https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/story/about-a-boy-hugh-grant-nicholas-hoult-interview-awards-insider"><i>《名利场》杂志</i></a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/nosferatu"><i>《诺斯费拉</i></a>图》主演<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/about-a-boy-stars-hugh-grant-and-nicholas-hoult-enjoy-reunion-22-years-later-3813649">尼古拉斯·霍尔特的重聚会上分享了这个故事，格兰特在霍尔特年仅 11 岁时曾与霍尔特一起出演过<i>《关于一个男孩》</i></a> 。</p><p>格兰特回忆道，在 2020 年完成<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/HBO">HBO 电视剧</a><i>《The Undoing》</i>的工作后，他在该剧杀青时送给了扮演他儿子的年轻演员诺亚·尤佩 (Noah Jupe) 一份礼物。</p><p>拍摄时朱佩 14 岁，格兰特送给他一盒雪茄作为感谢。</p><p>霍尔特回忆起 2002 年他从格兰特那里收到的包装礼物——一套高尔夫球杆。 “你从<i>About a Boy 那里得到了我的第一套球杆作为包装礼物。</i>你还记得吗？而且你还在高尔夫球袋上签名了，”他回忆道。</p><p>格兰特回应说，这是一份“迷人”的礼物，然后补充道：“这比我在<i>《毁灭》</i>中送给儿子的一盒雪茄包装礼物要好。他的母亲非常生气。”</p><p>您可以在这里观看两人重聚的视频： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="休·格兰特和尼古拉斯·霍尔特在《关于一个男孩》21年后重聚|名利场" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/3a6x6C0kNrM?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>近年来，霍尔特出演了 <i><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/renfield-review-nicolas-cage-dracula-3429190">《雷菲尔德》</a> 、《菜单》</i>和电视连续剧<i>《伟大》</i> ，并将出演即将上映的罗伯特·艾格斯的<i>《诺斯费拉</i>图》翻拍片，并在<i>《超人》</i>中扮演莱克斯·卢瑟。今年早些时候，他出现在克林特·伊斯特伍德的<i>《二号陪审员》中。</i></p><p>继<i>《关于一个男孩》</i>之后，霍尔特继续主演青少年连续剧<i>《皮肤》</i> ，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-interviews/nicholas-hoult-interview-renfield-skins-euphoria-3429639">于去年向<i>《NME》</i>建议</a>该剧“捕捉到了那个时刻——就像<i>《幸福感》</i>捕捉到了现在的时刻一样”。</p><p> “这很有趣，因为我记得我的 Skins 日子与<i>NME</i>紧密相连，”他补充道。 “有一年我参加了<i>NME</i>颁奖典礼，并见到了 Alex Turner，这非常令人兴奋，因为我喜欢 Arctic Monkeys。你们举办的聚会真的很有趣。</p><p> “我不记得[他说了什么]。另外，我可能喝醉了。谁知道？但我记得很开心。我仍然在某个地方保留着我们的照片，这很酷。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="休·格兰特 (Hugh Grant) 与特拉维斯·凯尔斯 (Travis Kelce) 一起演唱 Radiohead 的《Creep》和龙舌兰酒" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/pNRcEnwEUDw?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在其他新闻中，最近主演了<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/heretic-review-hugh-grant-horror-3807614"><i>《异端</i></a>》的格兰特回顾了他在 1999 年电影<i>《诺丁山》</i>中饰演的威廉·撒克，称他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/hugh-grant-calls-his-notting-hill-character-despicable-why-doesnt-he-have-any-balls-3813225">“卑鄙”</a> 。</p><p> “每当我喝了几杯酒后在家里翻看频道时，就会想到这个问题，我就会想，‘为什么我的角色没有任何胆量？’”他告诉 <a href="https://www.vanityfair.com/video/watch/scene-selection-vf-scene-selection-hugh-grant"><i>《名利场》</i>的场景选择</a>。 “这部电影中有一个场景，她在我家，爸爸来到前门按响了门铃，我想我只是让她从我身边走过，打开了门。太糟糕了。</p><p> “我从来没有一个女朋友，甚至现在的妻子，没有说过‘你到底为什么不阻止她？你这人怎么回事？&#39;我对此并没有真正的答案——它就是这样写的。我认为他真的很卑鄙。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/hugh-grant-gave-the-undoing-child-star-a-box-of-cigars-as-wrap-present-3819794">休·格兰特送给“The Undoing”童星一盒雪茄作为包装礼物：“他的母亲很愤怒”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
